data.description: Welcome home to this distinctly styled property that boasts a must see contemporary interior. The overall flow offers a zen like atmosphere with philosophically defined modern characteristics. This combined with an innovative design gives the home an artistic feel throughout. The well thought out landscaping has a decorative front pond that will provide serene sounds while sitting on the parasol style covered curved deck. The fenced in back yard has a raised patio and plenty of tall trees & vegetation to increase the privacy. Extra large windows in the front and rear of the home allow you to enjoy the views year round. Upon entering the home, you will first notice the graceful combination of elements & amenities that were artistically placed to add aesthetic appeal and inspiration. Several skylights provide lots of nature's light to flow in. The walkout lower level has an office/den, non-conforming fourth bedroom, full bathroom, sauna room, and doorway leading to your very own private nirvana. Don’t wait until this one is gone – book your private showing today!
